{"tid":325352,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[奇遇] 有冇人試過住酒店間房有打開咗嘅聖經？","createTime":"2017-07-17T07:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T10:22:01.000Z","uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75ffb13ee05aba3833038a468072ee16482e1322","tid":325352,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"啲人成日話如果見到有就要即刻換房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩自己暫時未遇過<br />\n聽我老母講佢好多年前去菲律賓旅行，住嗰間酒店房有四本聖經，其中兩本仲係打開嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢住落都相安無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲都試過呢類情況？或者聽人講過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a111d9c8d169b20f1456cc5a8af482392cbd4794","tid":325352,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:11:04.000Z","msg":"奴隸國係天主教國家，有聖經有乜問題？"},{"pid":"a9e7baee9327b1d2825c1399382dc78c65552d1c","tid":325352,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:14:18.000Z","msg":"信則有<br />\n不信則無<br />\n我由細到大都唔信<br />\n亦唔會刻意去搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c54fd335823688c5dde3d7ce452c3bd1bdb765","tid":325352,"uid":13283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:17:24.000Z","msg":"之前做酒店裝修，拆走啲櫃嗰時見到本聖經，貪得意拎咗嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0812dc78ebabb3ef29e510fddbc31ff0895c0f3a","tid":325352,"uid":21273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信則有<br />\n不信則無<br />\n我由細到大都唔信<br />\n亦唔會刻意去搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細細個去歐洲屋企人打開過一次，當晚驚到唔夠膽訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8154438bad097711c147f670487137ac89f0ea54","tid":325352,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:19:29.000Z","msg":"去ocamp嗰陣間房見到櫃桶有本打開左嘅聖經 之後揭吓睇吓 冇乜特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce95c742176503ab7c2032a24158b891bad938e7","tid":325352,"uid":64202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"同女朋友旅行 <br />\n我打開左睇比佢係咁罵<br />\n我又無做壞事 平時又有幫人 <br />\n我都唔知佢有咩好驚"},{"pid":"6a4072bdd74c62aafd84ab22bab3a9c9a184e13a","tid":325352,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奴隸國係天主教國家，有聖經有乜問題？</blockquote><br />\n但打開佢好似話係要驅鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705e1f2356105dfd5bccd8e7ec76ee152d443b9b","tid":325352,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同女朋友旅行 <br />\n我打開左睇比佢係咁罵<br />\n我又無做壞事 平時又有幫人 <br />\n我都唔知佢有咩好驚</blockquote><br />\n佢本身有冇宗教信仰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94be4ba91d2701aaa10f0282cd4595bf212a4dba","tid":325352,"uid":85840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"有仲要係尾房 除咗係冷氣凍啲之外但咩事都冇發生<br />\n反而冇聖經先出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e95dabd0b8a3f3b3ed8fba4aafb7dc4f2d0e7a","tid":325352,"uid":122867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:38:05.000Z","msg":"大家會唔會敲敲門先?"},{"pid":"ae1add5da2f052b6bba009ee3a824c9a411d2ef8","tid":325352,"uid":64202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同女朋友旅行 <br />\n我打開左睇比佢係咁罵<br />\n我又無做壞事 平時又有幫人 <br />\n我都唔知佢有咩好驚</blockquote><br />\n佢本身有冇宗教信仰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢咪信啲on9星座咁 應該唔算掛<br />\n<br />\n我自己之前接觸過基督教幾年 <br />\n已經睇曬成本聖經<br />\n最後都係覺得唔適合我先無再理"},{"pid":"c0058f2939ce3b7448df193fe3a902d19a3d74a8","tid":325352,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家會唔會敲敲門先?</blockquote><br />\n一定會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f2946582652fa6235351e370315e1b126ca360","tid":325352,"uid":22932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"試過跟學校旅行<br />\n幾個fd一齊訓尾房<br />\n我就撞損頭<br />\n有人就隻腳唔知做咩流血<br />\n跟住聽到門口有笑聲<br />\n但又見唔到有人<br />\n聽到兩次<br />\n但當時玩得太癲咩都唔知<br />\n後尾諗返先覺得"},{"pid":"7fb48fafd00f5e8a0f9e227dcb343c32edae1c55","tid":325352,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家會唔會敲敲門先?</blockquote><br />\n從來冇呢個習慣<br />\n<br />\n就算住頭尾房都係即入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89d4a2c7510561b975289b4fb29ccb96de3706e","tid":325352,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家會唔會敲敲門先?</blockquote><br />\n從來冇呢個習慣<br />\n<br />\n就算住頭尾房都係即入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n敲即係你假想左入面有野 即係你驚"},{"pid":"c0a6a85651e53163aeb5b44d2687cc59183af9fe","tid":325352,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家會唔會敲敲門先?</blockquote><br />\n一定會<img src=\"/assets/